snippet.title: SRB2 - OLDC Summer 2020
snippet.description:
This contain spoilers so its best you play it on your own if you haven't already. ._.

The Official Level Design Contest (OLDC) is back and here to bring out the newest creations upon the message board! 
This might be the longest video I have put out (would be longer if I didnt cut out the deaths (yes I suck XD)).
